description: Decibel Cannabis Company Inc. engages in the cultivation, processing, production, and retail sale of cannabis products in Canada. It offers cannabis flower, cannabis pre-rolls, and cannabis biomass to licensed producers in Canada. The company is also involved in the extraction, processing, and manufacturing of various cannabis derivative products, including vape cartridges, cannabis infused products, and cannabis extracts. It offers its products under the Qwest, Qwest Reserve, Blendcraft by Qwest, and General Admission brands. Decibel Cannabis Company Inc. is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
